title: Stress free Pillar Bedding (Richard Franklin)
description: This video will show you all the right supplies and tools required to do a precision bedding job. Richard shows how to properly relieve the bedding area to accept the bedding compound, how to make pillars, how to set up the barreled action and stock for stress free bedding. In this video Richard completely pillar beds a finished custom stock and also a Remington stock using the same tools available to anyone. Shows how to test your bedding job for being stress free. Many tips on pillars, stress free bedding and the supplies and tools needed to get a 100 % stress free job the first time.
